    <body>

        <div rend="parallel">
          <p xml:id="Kali121-kilavi">itu talaivaṉ oruvaḻit taṇantaviṭattut talaivi āṟṟāmai kūṟi varaiyak karutiṉāyāyiṉ iḵtiṭameṉac colliyatu.</p>
          <p xml:lang="en"></p>
        </div>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="Kali121">
                <l>oṇcuṭar kalcēra vulakūrun takaiyatu </l>
                <l>teṇkaṭa laḻuvattut tirainīkkā veḻutarūun </l>
                <l>taṇkatir matiyat taṇinilā niṟaittarap </l>
                <l>puḷḷiṉa miraimāntip pukalcēra voliyāṉṟu </l>
                <l>vaḷḷitaḻ kūmpiya maṇimaru ḷiruṅkaḻi </l>
                <l>paḷḷipuk katupōlum parappunīrt taṇcērppa; </l>
                <l rend="space">tāṅkaruṅ kāmattait taṇantunī puṟamāṟat </l>
                <l>tūṅkunī rimiḻtirai tuṇaiyāki yolikkumē </l>
                <l>yuṟaiyoṭu vaikiya pōtupō loyyeṉa </l>
                <l>niṟaiyāṉā tiḻitarūu nīrnīntu kaṇṇāṭku;</l>
                <l rend="space">vārāynī puṟamāṟa varuntiya mēṉiyāṭ </l>
                <l>kāriruṭ ṭuṇaiyāki yacaivaḷi yalaikkumē </l>
                <l>kamaḻtaṇṭā tutirntuka vūḻuṟṟa kōṭalvī </l>
                <l>yitaḻcōruṅ kulaipōla viṟainīvu vaḷaiyāṭku;</l>
                <l rend="space">iṉṟuṇai nīnīppa viraviṉuṭ ṭuṇaiyākit </l>
                <l>taṉṟuṇaip pirintayāan taṉikkuru kucavumē </l>
                <l>yoṇcuṭar ñāyiṟṟu viḷakkattā ṉoḷicāmpu </l>
                <l>naṇpakaṉ matiyampō ṉalañcāynta vaṇiyāṭku</l>
                <l>eṉavāṅku, </l>
                <l>eṟitirai tantiṭa viḻintamī ṉiṉṟuṟai </l>
                <l>maṟitirai varuntāmaṟ koṇṭāṅku neṟitāḻntu </l>
                <l>cāyiṉaḷ varuntiyā ḷiṭumpai </l>
                <l>pāyparik kaṭuntiṇṭēr kaḷaiyiṉō viṭaṉē.</l>
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
                <l corresp="6cd">O man from the cool coast with waters in an expanse,</l>
                <l corresp="3">while the ornate light of the cool-rayed moon becomes full</l>
                <l corresp="2">that rises without repelling the waves of the clear sea’s depth</l>
                <l corresp="1">in a suitable manner when the bright sun has joined the rocks,</l>
                <l corresp="4ab+6ab">flocks of birds having fed on [their] prey, seem to enter [their] resting-places</l>
                <l corresp="5">in the sapphire-like dark backwaters where the ample petals close,</l>
                <l corresp="4cd">without a sound when joining for entering:</l>
                <l>Cooling [her] passion difficult to bear when you shift to the outside</l>
                <l>the buzzing wave of the hanging water sound, being the companions</l>
                <l>of her with eyes swimming with water that falls in unending fulness</l>
                <l corresp="7-10">suddenly like buds that are kept with drops.</l>
                <l>Difficult darkness being [her] companion for the her with a body that suffers </l>
                <l>when you, not coming, have shifted to the outside, the moving wind harasses</l>
                <l>her with bangles that brush past [her] wrists like bunches of petals that drop</l>
                <l corresp="11-14">from flower that have past maturity when the fragrant cool pollen drops [and] is shed.</l>
                <l>Being [her] companion in the night when you have left your sweet mate</l>
                <l>a solitary heron on the water, separated from its mate, inquires</l>
                <l>from her with ornaments whose beauty has declined like the moon at high noon</l>
                <l corresp="15-18">when [its] brightness withers in the light of the bright glowing sun.</l>
                <l corresp="19">That is to say,</l>
                <l>sinking in on the path as if taking without suffering the overturning waves</l>
                <l>on the shore-line pleasing with fish the fall down [there] when brought by the dashing waves,</l>
                <l>if [you with] a fast firm chariot [with horses] of leaping motion were to remove</l>
                <l corresp="20-23">the affliction of her who suffers, being one who is emaciated, [now] is the moment. </l>
            </lg>
